<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>in the right • on the right</xh5><p> <i>in the right—</i>morally correct in one’s behavior or judgment: You are <u>in the right</u> in refusing to give in to them.</p><p> <i>on the right—</i>on the right side: Proceed for about one-half mile around a curve, passing three houses <u>on the right</u>.</p> </entry>
